### 獲取所有單字卡
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards

### 獲取特定單字卡
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards/1

### 創建新單字卡 - 漢字詞（漢語系）
POST https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "kanji": "水",
    "hiragana": "みず",
    "katakana": "",
    "meaning": "水",
    "example": "水を飲みます。",
    "wordType": 1,
    "difficulty": 1,
    "category": 4
}

### 創建新單字卡 - 外來語（片假名）
POST https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "kanji": "",
    "hiragana": "",
    "katakana": "テーブル",
    "meaning": "桌子",
    "example": "新しいテーブルを買いました。",
    "wordType": 2,
    "difficulty": 1,
    "category": 0
}

### 創建新單字卡 - 日文原生詞（平假名）
