### 更新單字卡
PUT https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "isFavorite": true,
    "katakana": "いぬ"
}

### 標記為已複習
POST https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards/1/review

### 獲取隨機單字卡
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards/random?count=3&category=1

### 獲取所有分類
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards/categories

### 獲取所有難度
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards/difficulties

### 獲取所有單字類型
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards/wordtypes

### 搜索單字卡（支援平假名和片假名）
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards?searchTerm=コーヒー&pageSize=5

### 按單字類型過濾 - 只顯示外來語
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards?wordType=2

### 按單字類型過濾 - 只顯示日文原生詞
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards?wordType=0

### 組合過濾 - 外來語 + 初學者難度
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards?wordType=2&difficulty=1

### 搜索平假名
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards?searchTerm=おはよう

### 搜索片假名
GET https://localhost:7777/api/flashcards?searchTerm=コンピューター
